8 Yeap .	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Robin .
9 Bye !	Have a nice day !

4 May I have a black tea ?	Which size ?
5 Medium , please .	Would you like anything else with that ?
6 Could I get a carrot cake , please ?	So that would be a medium black tea and a carrot cake . Is that right ?
7 Can I have an Earl Grey , please ?	Sure ! So that would be a medium Earl Grey and a carrot cake . Is that right ?
8 Actually , I would like an almond croissant instead .	Sure ! So that would be a medium Earl Grey and an almond croissant . Is that right ?
9 Yeah .	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Kiefer .
10 Thanks !	Have a nice day !

8 Yes !	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Ellen .
9 Goodbye !	Have a nice day !

7 Definitely .	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Jeffrey .
8 Cheers !	Have a nice day !
